</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Bridges" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A slightly long exposure, taken from the Nakanoshima Bridge. 中之島大橋から撮影した少し長めの露出。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2506_A7R04719_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2506_A7R04719_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Evening Walk・夕方の散歩</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250601/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Evening Walk・夕方の散歩" /><published>2025-06-01T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-06-01T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/evening-walk</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250601/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
