</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[First sunlight hits a cluster of reeds along the Katsura River, in front of the Togetsukyo bridge. 桂川沿いの葦の群れに、最初の陽光が当たります。その先には、渡月橋が見えます。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_A7R04571.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_A7R04571.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Morning in the Grove</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250527/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Morning in the Grove" /><published>2025-05-27T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-05-27T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/chikurin</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250527/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
